{"tid":1721864,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"內地學生係大陸被罵真係好慘","createTime":"2019-11-14T18:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:32:45.000Z","uid":293575,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"922fb593c64cd7d344593cd14d340011633efead","tid":1721864,"uid":293575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:54:01.000Z","msg":"唔好意思。我都明白依家有好多要緊的嘢，內地生哩個topic可能真係冇人關心。<br />\n<br />\n但我好想話俾大家知，其實內地生都有黃絲。（哩兩張圖係一個人嘅朋友圈同佢在下邊留下嘅評論，為咗隱去名字我裁減咗圖片。）（<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/1400255260/Ig3XHnL4R?type=comment#_rnd1573750857863）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.com%2F1400255260%2FIg3XHnL4R%3Ftype%3Dcomment%23_rnd1573750857863%EF%BC%89&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=ef82dfbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.com/1400255260/Ig3XHnL4R?type=comment#_rnd1573750857863）</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azigrJn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazigrJn.png&h=092f73ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9B7H6Jo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9B7H6Jo.png&h=dbd2cd02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩幾句說話在連登看都好平常，但佢就因此在微博上被起底痛罵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnQiE4w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmnQiE4w.png&h=c68dee37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8TU7ypS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8TU7ypS.png&h=fd405182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明白好多大陸學生係偏藍嘅，但其實留學生裡黃絲嘅比例肯定係高過內地平均水平。只係黃絲好難發聲，哪怕只係淺黃說幾句真心話，都好驚被起底。<br />\n<br />\n譬如哩個中大女生，因為接受港台採訪時說：&ldquo;我覺得還沒有嚴重到要逃難&ldquo;，就被罵到寫公開信道歉的程度。（<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/mn8mho6klEDCjApo1kns3g）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2Fmn8mho6klEDCjApo1kns3g%EF%BC%89&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=6929bb0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/mn8mho6klEDCjApo1kns3g）</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQ2hbbB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQ2hbbB.png&h=663c792e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwnXVDm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnwnXVDm.png&h=d7668eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5bE8Yo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5bE8Yo.png&h=44669e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SX9rOYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSX9rOYr.jpg&h=2da664c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7HVRZ5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HVRZ5f.png&h=2e36b15d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FchbbX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FchbbX.jpg&h=96f1262e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FQ2Udqi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQ2Udqi.jpg&h=3952f79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKyHniE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKyHniE.png&h=3c868728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁都會被罵成&ldquo;被奴化&rdquo;：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpWxKxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpWxKxG.png&h=29d72a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AfghVEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAfghVEo.jpg&h=b8075776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都明白在大家看來內地學生係藍絲、係逃兵，其實陸生真係兩面不是人。內地主流輿論宜家越來越深藍，因此哪怕係淺藍都俾佢啲罵。<br />\n<br />\n中大內地生之前就因為報導偏頗的事情同內地網友吵過一架，宜家又因為環球時報不提local對佢啲嘅幫助而和記者鬧翻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Sw54xU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Sw54xU.jpg&h=6dce15c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就連科大MSSS咁藍嘅組織都因為在聲明裡提到&ldquo;味道刺鼻的催泪瓦斯&rdquo;同感謝學校而被罵緊（<a href=\"https://weibo.com/jeune?is_hot=1#1573754856114）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2Fjeune%3Fis_hot%3D1%231573754856114%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=46f87fb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://weibo.com/jeune?is_hot=1#1573754856114）。</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnYj8ZB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnYj8ZB.png&h=c8c3a24f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajvVHjE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FajvVHjE.png&h=737cdd75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有內地其實有好多黃絲網友，只係唔敢太明顯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJ4GCTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJ4GCTa.jpg&h=6d9020e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家多一分理解，唔好一棒子打死所有的內地人。<br />\n<br />\nwe connect <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外相關的有：<br />\n<br />\n立場發的一封內地交換生公開信：<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/內地在港交流生-被有關部門強行安排全部遣返/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E7%94%9F-%E8%A2%AB%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E5%BC%B7%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%81%A3%E8%BF%94%2F&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=f6a2ca35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E7%94%9F-%E8%A2%AB%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E5%BC%B7%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%81%A3%E8%BF%94%2F&h=9ed98e70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/內地在港交流生-被有關部門強行安排全部遣返/</a><br />\n<br />\n中大陸生《留駐獨家村》：<a href=\"https://matters.news/@bluefloydwong0525/留駐獨家村-zdpuB2hpzgr2ZiBt14r8F8DBtnnpPiwD7kgwrXig4WG2j4Mzr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatters.news%2F%40bluefloydwong0525%2F%E7%95%99%E9%A7%90%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%9D%91-zdpuB2hpzgr2ZiBt14r8F8DBtnnpPiwD7kgwrXig4WG2j4Mzr&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=419c58b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://matters.news/@bluefloydwong0525/留駐獨家村-zdpuB2hpzgr2ZiBt14r8F8DBtnnpPiwD7kgwrXig4WG2j4Mzr</a>"},{"pid":"f7ca51fbc839075a3927f4502744d6df9a2ed2b8","tid":1721864,"uid":53143,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:59:25.000Z","msg":"係，其實仲有好多大陸嘅係黃，不過就冇咁勇係大陸嚮哂口咁講"},{"pid":"97a7763e3b41cd88178cd106cabd561335001927","tid":1721864,"uid":307249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:16:39.000Z","msg":"Noted with thx"},{"pid":"fa3b73ff61176009f702b592fc6ea6f4f5c86989","tid":1721864,"uid":21468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:16:46.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"5c90572b50b4559fe4f8122139424c9fc4c38241","tid":1721864,"uid":3358,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:17:38.000Z","msg":"係支那講呢d =係街打狗咁勇武嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32959f5f8e45eb79013a2434f2b1d405aaccbad0","tid":1721864,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:18:21.000Z","msg":"小心啲啊大陸生<br />\n保住條命"},{"pid":"efc0d2d1f118d7848d306b80bd7f5f5cb57aaca9","tid":1721864,"uid":109115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5c90572b50b4559fe4f8122139424c9fc4c38241","tid":1721864,"uid":3358,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:17:38.000Z","msg":"係支那講呢d =係街打狗咁勇武嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:21:03.000Z","msg":"另類勇武 <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor